channel.title: Website Template (First One I Ever Made)
channel.description:
Ok so i was learning HTML and CSS and decided to make a website template, this is the first i ever made so please dont hate...
This template is only colored in #333-#999 because i like grey. So yeah, here it is (its kind of shitty i know...)
[IMG]http://i1062.photobucket.com/albums/t499/202685/Template.png[/img]
It can currently hold 15 links (it will change if you change the logo size...
Yeah i know its not 'good looking' but atleast i tried... please don't hate
P.S. The reason there is a random "HI" behind the textarea is because i messed up lol, you can just delete that, (its in the field "body1")
